		- appstat.jvm.GcPsScavengeCount：JVM垃圾回收次数
		- appstat.jvm.GcPsMarkSweepCount：JVM标记清除次数
		- appstat.jvm.GcG1OldGenCount：JVM_Old区G1GC次数
